          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Bob and Angie Shepherd recently had their car stolen, which sucks, obviously. But the situation got even worse when the traffic tickets started to pile up. Their stolen car was used in a crime spree, and they’re having to sort this one out in order to fight back.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "“So I get up in the morning and I’m going to work,” Bob Shepherd said. “Her car is not there.”",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
